### Get all transfers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/transfers

### Create a new transfer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.00,
  "sourceId": 1,
  "targetId": 2
}

### Create transfer with validation error (negative amount)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/transfers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": -25.00,
  "sourceId": 1,
  "targetId": 2
}